original_title: UFC Fight Night 74: Holloway vs. Oliveira
overview: UFC Fight Night 74: Holloway vs. Oliveira was a mixed martial arts event held on August 23, 2015 at the SaskTel Centre in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, Canada. The event was headlined by a featherweight bout between rising stars Max Holloway and Charles Oliveira.
title: UFC Fight Night 74: Holloway vs. Oliveira
